I used the food processor for this wonderfully easy and flavorful cake. Place butter, sugar, egg, vanilla and buttermilk in bowl of food processor and process until well mixed. Add previously-blended dry ingredients to the processor bowl and pulse briefly until blended. Do not overprocess. Dot raspberries over the surface of the cake, using about one and a half cups of berries. The cake turned out of the pan beautifully. People loved this cake.

